Canada, uses a statistical approach to evaluate the environmental performance of marine aquaculture.[/grid]\r\n\r\n[grid image=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/GraphicOceana.gif\" title=\"Oceana\"]Oceana supported a conference held in Belize in 2011 aimed at disseminating and repatriating crucial information on the marine biodiversity and fisheries of Belize and what the people of Belize were at risk to lose due to proposed oil exploration in their waters.[/grid]\r\n','Collaborations','','inherit','closed','open','','3325-revision-v1','','','2015-03-30 14:27:19','2015-03-30 21:27:19','',3325,'http://wordpress.dev/3325-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(3417,12,'2015-03-30 14:30:07','2015-03-30 21:30:07','<h1>Partners</h1>\r\n\r\n[grid link=\"http://www.vulcan.com\" image=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/GraphicVulcan.gif\" title=\"Vulcan/PGA Family Foundation\"]Vulcan, a Paul G. Allen company, is a nimble private company with a portfolio as diverse as the challenges of the world. Vulcan’s philanthropic group invests in projects that advance discovery and catalyze great ideas that drive positive change for life on the planet.[/grid]\r\n\r\n[grid link=\"/data/#/topic/biodiversity\" image=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/GraphicFishbase1.gif\" title=\"FishBase/SeaLifeBase\"]Global databases with detailed information on fishes (FishBase) and all other marine organisms (SeaLifeBase).[/grid]\r\n\r\n[grid link=\"http://www.pewtrusts.org/en\" image=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/GraphicPew.gif\" title=\"The Pew Charitable Trusts\"]The Pew Charitable Trusts initiated the Sea Around Us and supported it for 15 years, and we continue to collaborate on various initiatives.[/grid]\r\n\r\n[grid link=\"/feru/\" image=\"/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/GraphicFERU.gif\" title=\"Fisheries Economics Research Unit\"]Long-standing collaboration with the Fisheries Economics Research Unit on all aspects related to fisheries economics.[/grid]\r\n\r\n[grid link=\"/climate-change\" image=\"/wp-content/uploa